Package Project

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Main
    Application to be invoked by the client.
    Model
    Implements the required methods to communicate the Genetic Algorithm related objects with the graphical components and the user interactions
    ParameterSelectionController
    Controller for the Parameter Selection View, handles events generated by the user
    SceneMediator
    Concrete implementation of a Mediator that handle and redirect requests from a set of objects that should exchange information among each other This is done in order to reduce the number of connections required in the application.
    SimulationController
    Controller for the Simulation View, handles the events generated by the user
